---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

---

<BaseLayout 
  title="404 迷路了啦！｜GAME8LA"
  description="你走錯路了啦鄉民！這個頁面不存在，快回首頁繼續看遊戲評測。"
  ogImage="https://game8la.com/images/og-image.webp"
  currentPage="home"
>
<!-- NAVBAR -->
<!-- 404 CONTENT -->
<main class="error-wrapper">
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-img">
      <img src="/images/index/game8la-404-mascot.webp" alt="GAME8LA 404 芭樂子迷路了">
    </div>
    <div class="error-text">
      <div class="error-code">404</div>
      <h1 class="error-title">哈囉？這頁被吃掉了啦！</h1>
      <p class="error-msg">
        鄉民你好，你找的頁面已經<span class="pink">被芭樂子啃光了</span>，
        可能是連結打錯、頁面搬家、或是被 Bug 怪獸吞掉了。<br><br>
        別慌！<span class="highlight">GAME8LA</span> 首頁還有一堆好料等你挖，
        老虎機評測、百家樂攻略、荷官排行榜⋯⋯全部免費看到飽。
      </p>
      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn-back">
          <i class="fas fa-home"></i> 帶我回首頁
        </a>
        <a href="/#ranking" class="btn-ranking">
          <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> 看遊戲排行榜
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="easter-egg">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <strong>芭樂子小提示：</strong>你可以用首頁上方的搜尋功能找到想看的遊戲，或是直接逛逛我們的遊戲排行榜，說不定會發現比你原本要找的更香的東西。
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
<!-- FOOTER -->
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --bg-primary: #121212;
  --guava-green: #39FF14;
  --guava-green-dark: #2bcc10;
  --guava-pink: #FF10F0;
  --text-primary: #FFFFFF;
  --text-secondary: #cccccc;
  --border: #2a2a2a;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 10%, rgba(57,255,20,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 30%, rgba(255,16,240,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 70%, rgba(57,255,20,0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #121212 30%, #0e120e 60%, #121212 100%);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* === NAVBAR === */
.navbar {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
  background: rgba(18,18,18,0.95);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 2rem;
  height: 64px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.navbar a {
  text-decoration: none;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}
.navbar img {
  height: 40px;
}
.nav-home {
  color: var(--guava-green);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}
.nav-home:hover { color: #fff; }

/* === MAIN 404 CONTENT === */
.error-wrapper {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 100px 1.5rem 3rem;
}
.error-container {
  max-width: 900px;
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 3rem;
}
.error-img {
  flex: 0 0 340px;
  text-align: center;
}
.error-img img {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 340px;
  height: auto;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(57,255,20,0.3)) drop-shadow(0 0 60px rgba(255,16,240,0.15));
  animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
}

.error-text {
  flex: 1;
}
.error-code {
  font-size: 7rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--guava-green), var(--guava-pink));
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  text-shadow: none;
}
.error-title {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.error-msg {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.error-msg .highlight {
  color: var(--guava-green);
  font-weight: 700;
}
.error-msg .pink {
  color: var(--guava-pink);
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* Buttons */
.error-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.btn-back {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--guava-green), var(--guava-green-dark));
  color: #000;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57,255,20,0.3);
}
.btn-back:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(57,255,20,0.5);
}
.btn-ranking {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--guava-pink);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--guava-pink);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.btn-ranking:hover {
  background: rgba(255,16,240,0.1);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,16,240,0.3);
}

/* Easter egg hint */
.easter-egg {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: rgba(57,255,20,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.15);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.easter-egg i {
  color: var(--guava-green);
  margin-right: 0.3rem;
}

/* === FOOTER === */
.footer-mini {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: #666;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}
.footer-mini a {
  color: var(--guava-green);
  text-decoration: none;
}

/* === MOBILE === */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .error-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .error-img {
    flex: none;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .error-img img {
    max-width: 260px;
  }
  .error-code {
    font-size: 5rem;
  }
  .error-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .error-actions {
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .easter-egg {
    text-align: left;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 420px) {
  .error-code {
    font-size: 4rem;
  }
  .error-img img {
    max-width: 200px;
  }
  .error-actions {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .btn-back, .btn-ranking {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }
}

</style>

<script is:inline>

</script>
